  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "ISM / SMS Coordinator",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Job Opening: ISM / SMS Coordinator (DOC & SMC Documentation)</strong></h2><h3><strong>Position Summary</strong></h3><p>We are seeking a detail-oriented <strong>ISM / SMS Coordinator</strong> to manage and maintain documentation related to <strong>DOC (Document of Compliance)</strong> and <strong>SMC (Safety Management Certificate)</strong> in accordance with the <strong>ISM Code</strong>. This role focuses on documentation, compliance support, and coordination with vessels, class societies, and relevant authorities.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare, maintain, and control <strong>DOC & SMC documentation</strong> in compliance with the ISM Code</p></li><li><p>Support implementation and continuous improvement of the <strong>Safety Management System (SMS)</strong></p></li><li><p>Coordinate ISM-related matters between vessels and shore management</p></li><li><p>Assist with <strong>internal and external audits</strong> (Flag State, Class, PSC, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Manage corrective and preventive actions (CAPA) related to ISM audits</p></li><li><p>Maintain records, manuals, procedures, and safety reports</p></li><li><p>Support the DPA in ISM compliance and safety management activities</p></li></ul>",
